Interface Vector3

All Superinterfaces:
Vector2
All Known Implementing Classes:
Vector3.Observable, Vector3.ReadOnly, Vector3.Value
public interface Vector3 extends Vector2
A head at some point in 3 dimensions and tail at (0, 0, 0).
